snippet.title: Worm War I for the Atari 2600
snippet.description:
Nice, but repetitive game.

However, it has some cool unique features, like the gas stations you can either blow up to destroy every single worm on the screen or to drive through and refuel and some "blockades" which you have to shoot or avoid.
